88c5ab5ecdcaee145e075be9e5e4","tid":498342,"uid":47359,"like":39,"dislike":4,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"本post五毛<br />\n1霍金轉身<br />\n2吾系甘開心牙"},{"pid":"c964b5a2499a8cb4b17625a6429078b3b08456ed","tid":498342,"uid":49388,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"粉絲年齡層最廣嘅政治人物係咪黃毓民?"},{"pid":"26911c2650ee833bf362fc018d954d3d73f74703","tid":498342,"uid":154783,"like":9,"dislike":66,"score":-57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"著成咁係連儂牆徘徊，俾龜逗都唔出奇<br />\n見到你有支類似槍既野，唔理三七二十一拉左先講，如果真係有傷害性咁放走左就好大獲<br />\n拉完俾個疑犯屌老母，我都警犬都磨你耐啲啦<br />\n<br />\n結論係衰戇鳩，下次做野做得好睇啲，咪乜事都無"},{"pid":"d4c0e71475ca8318e8fbcbf74eaa0030539f5f79","tid":498342,"uid":43042,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"條友真係好撚慘<br />\n可能平時上連登見港獨po幾千個正評以為好撚疊馬<br />\n點知出到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8673e6fd6173ce05ec653e0bbff85a6d651f6ae9","tid":498342,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"學下連登獨派代表HKVDC_2017咁，帶美軍止血劑嘛"},{"pid":"9f71d6f1a8af901dc95143876319faee87a7af0d","tid":498342,"uid":16676,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"若警方持有裁判官發出的手令（又稱搜查令），<br />\n他們可進入任何單位進行搜查。<br />\n警方須以宣誓方式向裁判官提出證據，<br />\n證明他們<span style=\"color: red;\">有理由懷疑在某建築物或地方內，<br />\n藏有任何有調查價值的物品。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q5.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FpoliceAndCrime%2Fpolice_powers%2Fq5.shtml&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNso9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ad4e3e9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q5.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n搜屋要搜查令<br />\n要法庭批準<br />\n<br />\n有搜查令既話就唔使打電話搵人老母啦<br />\n擺明黑警打比佢屋企人想嚇佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72f5a4b4ec3ef39007c45a4104f8ac042a28978","tid":498342,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:35:30.000Z","msg":"睇嚟帶翻生果刀安全啲"},{"pid":"43e233778d71b1ea698de25501994296038674c3","tid":498342,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友真係好撚慘<br />\n可能平時上連登見港獨po幾千個正評以為好撚疊馬<br />\n點知出到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢都算醒，唔回應班猶差，廢事中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過帶支玩具槍做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5968f293681116387db0e5d0803d8a9a86c87c9","tid":498342,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:40:49.000Z","msg":"對警犬唔需要講任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a573e223f16e3f32a105e8ef201d955d56be9686","tid":498342,"uid":142965,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/014155_23bd3404ba2b7b9cc75f4420ea98f621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F014155_23bd3404ba2b7b9cc75f4420ea98f621.jpg&h=b4f1ea1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4eaa40f5788ab7d434824a0bd33d10d98c83715d","tid":498342,"uid":34103,"like":16,"dislike":36,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da562d9096a5ae21957e799f8f55264cf7c9522f","tid":498342,"uid":69681,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"如果單單係涉嫌藏有仿制槍械而拉既話我覺得冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先從外表係唔會一眼就確定到係真槍定假槍<br />\n第二就算係氣槍都未知會唔會過法定焦耳<br />\n反上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申非五毛理性討論"},{"pid":"dc6698bc5abe2f4d9697aea4f8268508ce6dc8b4","tid":498342,"uid":53577,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果單單係涉嫌藏有仿制槍械而拉既話我覺得冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先從外表係唔會一眼就確定到係真槍定假槍<br />\n第二就算係氣槍都未知會唔會過法定焦耳<br />\n反上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申非五毛理性討論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白痴，係咪見親bb槍就拎去驗？咁多書局唔收晒啲槍去驗？<br />\n而家擺明係屈，睇下有冇罪入到你，見支槍咁流，就想去佢屋企摷cp,  確認佢住址可能就係準備揾黑警hacker插贓。"},{"pid":"075e56fcd6165f4b6f1f856845fef57f73d05ac8","tid":498342,"uid":88134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢冇超過法定能量冇理由拉佢，如果咁都拉得旺角賣氣槍咪大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樣槍佢就收撚左你<br />\n拎到返去2焦耳改到20焦耳都得<br />\n要砌你容乜易"},{"pid":"b6d16f703b9d75f29850c41a84b80514c01bb45c","tid":498342,"uid":47359,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為自己挑戰法律好撚型<br />\n點知到最後個個當你condom冇人幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛dewi</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/024235_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F024235_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=87ea65b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f38bc76808cb789806e247e4a5465ceefedd34c7","tid":498342,"uid":3465,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/024236_c25ff1cbd2f3394974bfcf59eb317aab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F024236_c25ff1cbd2f3394974bfcf59eb317aab.jpg&h=5b9a959a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/024249_5bc9a9f799410e9d7bedb59d2c9e3683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F024249_5bc9a9f799410e9d7bedb59d2c9e3683.jpg&h=6839ccf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c068c477622c922ae477caccfa251b7024c250b","tid":498342,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>若警方持有裁判官發出的手令（又稱搜查令），<br />\n他們可進入任何單位進行搜查。<br />\n警方須以宣誓方式向裁判官提出證據，<br />\n證明他們<span style=\"color: red;\">有理由懷疑在某建築物或地方內，<br />\n藏有任何有調查價值的物品。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q5.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FpoliceAndCrime%2Fpolice_powers%2Fq5.shtml&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNso9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ad4e3e9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q5.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n搜屋要搜查令<br />\n要法庭批準<br />\n<br />\n有搜查令既話就唔使打電話搵人老母啦<br />\n擺明黑警打比佢屋企人想嚇佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實申請搜查令好易好快<br />\n所以行動者要早有準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過犯法嘢唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bde24696b5dae979ec03ea08e070b439710d78a","tid":498342,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢冇超過法定能量冇理由拉佢，如果咁都拉得旺角賣氣槍咪大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc